  "body": "\n\n<div class=\"oscl-hero\">\n<div class=\"oscl-hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"oscl-grid\">\n<div class=\"oscl-left\">\n<div class=\"oscl-eyebrow oscl-anim-y\"><div class=\"oscl-eyebrow-dot\"></div><span class=\"oscl-eyebrow-txt\">Free Construction Calculators</span></div>\n<h1 class=\"oscl-h1 oscl-anim-y oscl-d1\">Calculate Faster.<span class=\"oscl-h1-em\">Build Smarter.</span></h1>\n<p class=\"oscl-sub oscl-anim-y oscl-d2\">Free, IS code-based calculators for steel, bricks, paint, and more. Built for Indian construction teams — instant quantity estimates, no spreadsheets needed.</p>\n<div class=\"oscl-features oscl-anim-y oscl-d3\">\n<div class=\"oscl-feat-pill\"><div class=\"oscl-feat-check\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"9\" viewbox=\"0 0 10 10\" width=\"9\"><path d=\"M2 5l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"oscl-feat-txt\">IS code formulas</span></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-feat-pill\"><div class=\"oscl-feat-check\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"9\" viewbox=\"0 0 10 10\" width=\"9\"><path d=\"M2 5l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"oscl-feat-txt\">Instant results</span></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-feat-pill\"><div class=\"oscl-feat-check\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"9\" viewbox=\"0 0 10 10\" width=\"9\"><path d=\"M2 5l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"oscl-feat-txt\">100% free</span></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-feat-pill\"><div class=\"oscl-feat-check\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"9\" viewbox=\"0 0 10 10\" width=\"9\"><path d=\"M2 5l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"oscl-feat-txt\">No sign-up</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-btns oscl-anim-y oscl-d4\">\n<a class=\"oscl-btn-primary\" href=\"#calculators\">Browse Calculators ↓</a>\n<a class=\"oscl-btn-outline\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">Try SiteFlow ERP Free</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-trust oscl-anim-y oscl-d5\">\n<span class=\"oscl-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n<span class=\"oscl-trust-txt\">Trusted by <strong>10,000+</strong> construction companies across India</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-right oscl-anim-x oscl-d1\">\n<div class=\"oscl-chrome\">\n<div class=\"oscl-dots\"><div class=\"oscl-dot\" style=\"background:#ff5f57!important;\"></div><div class=\"oscl-dot\" style=\"background:#febc2e!important;\"></div><div class=\"oscl-dot\" style=\"background:#28c840!important;\"></div></div>\n<span class=\"oscl-chrome-title\">SiteFlow · Steel Calculator for Column</span>\n<div class=\"oscl-chrome-badge\"><div class=\"oscl-chrome-badge-dot\"></div><span class=\"oscl-chrome-badge-txt\">AI Ready</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-dash\">\n<div class=\"oscl-tabs\">\n<div class=\"oscl-tab oscl-tab-active\">🏛 Column</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-tab oscl-tab-idle\">One-Way Slab</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-tab oscl-tab-idle\">Two-Way Slab</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-input-card\">\n<div class=\"oscl-card-header\"><span class=\"oscl-card-lbl\">Column Dimensions</span><span class=\"oscl-badge oscl-badge-p\">IS 456</span></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-input-rows\">\n<div class=\"oscl-input-row\">\n<div class=\"oscl-input-field\"><div class=\"oscl-field-lbl\">Column Height</div><div class=\"oscl-field-val\">3000 <span class=\"oscl-field-val-muted\">mm</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-input-field\"><div class=\"oscl-field-lbl\">Slab Thickness</div><div class=\"oscl-field-val\">150 <span class=\"oscl-field-val-muted\">mm</span></div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-input-row\">\n<div class=\"oscl-input-field\"><div class=\"oscl-field-lbl\">Column Size (a)</div><div class=\"oscl-field-val\">450 <span class=\"oscl-field-val-muted\">mm</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-input-field\"><div class=\"oscl-field-lbl\">Column Size (b)</div><div class=\"oscl-field-val\">300 <span class=\"oscl-field-val-muted\">mm</span></div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-input-row\">\n<div class=\"oscl-input-field\"><div class=\"oscl-field-lbl\">Main Bar Dia</div><div class=\"oscl-field-val\">20 <span class=\"oscl-field-val-muted\">mm · 4 nos</span></div></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-input-field\"><div class=\"oscl-field-lbl\">Stirrup Dia</div><div class=\"oscl-field-val\">8 <span class=\"oscl-field-val-muted\">mm @ 150</span></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-results-card\">\n<div class=\"oscl-card-header\"><span class=\"oscl-card-lbl\">Calculated Result</span><span class=\"oscl-badge oscl-badge-g\">Ready</span></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-results-grid\">\n<div class=\"oscl-result-cell\"><div class=\"oscl-result-n\">65.55</div><div class=\"oscl-result-l\">Main bars (kg)</div></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-result-cell\"><div class=\"oscl-result-n\">18.42</div><div class=\"oscl-result-l\">Stirrups (kg)</div></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-result-cell\"><div class=\"oscl-result-n oscl-result-n-g\">83.97</div><div class=\"oscl-result-l\">Total weight (kg)</div></div>\n<div class=\"oscl-result-cell\"><div class=\"oscl-result-n oscl-result-n-g\">₹5,040</div><div class=\"oscl-result-l\">Est. cost</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscl-is-note\"><div class=\"oscl-is-dot\"></div><span class=\"oscl-is-txt\">Formula: D² ÷ 163 · IS 456:2000 compliant · includes 5% wastage</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<span id=\"calculators\" style=\"display:block!important;height:0!important;\"></span>\n<div class=\"osclg-outer\">\n<div class=\"osclg-inner\">\n<div class=\"osclg-head\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"osclg-eyebrow\"><div class=\"osclg-eyebrow-dot\"></div><span class=\"osclg-eyebrow-txt\">All Calculators</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"osclg-h2\">Pick your calculator</h2>\n<p class=\"osclg-h2-sub\">All formulas follow IS code. Results are instant.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"osclg-filters\">\n<button class=\"osclg-fbtn osclg-on\" data-filter=\"all\">All</button>\n<button class=\"osclg-fbtn\" data-filter=\"steel\">Steel and RCC</button>\n<button class=\"osclg-fbtn\" data-filter=\"masonry\">Masonry</button>\n<button class=\"osclg-fbtn\" data-filter=\"finishes\">Finishes</button>\n</div>\n Grid — fully populated by JS. No hardcoded cards. \n<div class=\"osclg-grid\" id=\"osclg-grid\">\n<div class=\"osclg-loading\">\n<div class=\"osclg-loading-dots\">\n<div class=\"osclg-loading-dot\"></div>\n<div class=\"osclg-loading-dot\"></div>\n<div class=\"osclg-loading-dot\"></div>\n</div>\n        Loading calculators…\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"oscls-outer\">\n<div class=\"oscls-inner\">\n<div class=\"oscls-card-r\">\n<div class=\"oscls-r-inner\">\n<div class=\"oscls-r-eyebrow\"><div class=\"oscls-r-eyebrow-dot\"></div><span class=\"oscls-r-eyebrow-txt\">Request a Calculator</span></div>\n<h3 class=\"oscls-r-h3\">Don’t see what you need?</h3>\n<p class=\"oscls-r-sub\">Tell us which calculator would save your team the most time. We build based on what contractors actually ask for.</p>\n<div class=\"oscls-usecases\">\n<div class=\"oscls-uc\"><div class=\"oscls-uc-dot\"></div>Footing steel</div>\n<div class=\"oscls-uc\"><div class=\"oscls-uc-dot\"></div>Staircase steel</div>\n<div class=\"oscls-uc\"><div class=\"oscls-uc-dot\"></div>Tile quantity</div>\n<div class=\"oscls-uc\"><div class=\"oscls-uc-dot\"></div>RCC beam</div>\n<div class=\"oscls-uc\"><div class=\"oscls-uc-dot\"></div>Waterproofing</div>\n<div class=\"oscls-uc\"><div class=\"oscls-uc-dot\"></div>Flooring</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"oscls-r-btns\">\n<a class=\"oscls-r-btn-primary\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">Suggest a Calculator</a>\n<a class=\"oscls-r-btn-ghost\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/contact/\">Contact Us</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n FAQ \n<div class=\"osclf-outer\">\n<div class=\"osclf-inner\">\n<div class=\"osclf-head osclf-anim\">\n<div class=\"osclf-eyebrow\"><div class=\"osclf-eyebrow-dot\"></div><span class=\"osclf-eyebrow-txt\">FAQ</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"osclf-h2\">Questions about these calculators</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"osclf-grid\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/FAQPage\">\n<div class=\"osclf-item osclf-anim\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"osclf-btn\" onclick=\"osclfToggle(this)\"><span class=\"osclf-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Are these calculators free to use?</span><span class=\"osclf-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"osclf-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"osclf-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes, completely free. No sign-up, no login, no limit on how many times you use them. All calculators on this page are built and maintained by SiteFlow and are available to anyone working in Indian construction.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"osclf-item osclf-anim osclf-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"osclf-btn\" onclick=\"osclfToggle(this)\"><span class=\"osclf-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Which IS code standards do the steel calculators follow?</span><span class=\"osclf-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"osclf-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"osclf-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">All steel calculators use IS 456:2000 formulas. The unit weight formula is D² ÷ 163 (kg/m), where D is bar diameter in mm. Lap lengths are calculated as 50D for columns. Stirrup cutting lengths account for 90° and 135° bend deductions as per IS standards. The Bar Bending Schedule calculator also follows SP 34 guidelines for shape codes.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"osclf-item osclf-anim\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"osclf-btn\" onclick=\"osclfToggle(this)\"><span class=\"osclf-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">What is the difference between the one-way slab and two-way slab calculators?</span><span class=\"osclf-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"osclf-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"osclf-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">A one-way slab (Ly/Lx greater than 2) carries load in the shorter direction only. Main bars run along the shorter span; distribution bars run in the longer direction. A two-way slab (Ly/Lx of 2 or less) carries load in both directions, so main reinforcement is needed along both Lx and Ly. Use the one-way calculator for beams spanning in one direction and the two-way for panels supported on all four sides.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"osclf-item osclf-anim osclf-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"osclf-btn\" onclick=\"osclfToggle(this)\"><span class=\"osclf-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Does the brick calculator account for mortar and wastage?</span><span class=\"osclf-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"osclf-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"osclf-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes. The brick calculator adds a 10 mm mortar joint to both length and height when counting bricks. It also calculates wet and dry mortar volume separately, then breaks that down into cement bags and sand quantity using a 1:6 mix ratio. Wastage is adjustable — the default is 10%, which covers standard site cutting. Decorative or diagonal brickwork should use 15 to 20%.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"osclf-item osclf-anim\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"osclf-btn\" onclick=\"osclfToggle(this)\"><span class=\"osclf-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How accurate are the paint quantity estimates?</span><span class=\"osclf-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"osclf-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"osclf-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">The paint calculator uses standard coverage rates: putty at 1.3 kg per m² for two coats, primer at 9 L per m² for one coat, and finish paint at 6.5 L per m² for two coats. These match the coverage figures used by most Indian paint brands on their technical data sheets. Results will be close to actual consumption for smooth plastered surfaces. Textured or rough surfaces will use more — add 10 to 15% in those cases.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"osclf-item osclf-anim osclf-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"osclf-btn\" onclick=\"osclfToggle(this)\"><span class=\"osclf-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">What does the Bar Bending Schedule calculator produce?</span><span class=\"osclf-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"osclf-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"osclf-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">It generates a complete BBS table with bar mark, bar type, diameter, shape code, cutting length, number of bars, and total weight per bar mark. The output follows the format used on most Indian construction sites and can be exported for procurement or site use. The AI layer helps verify shape codes and flag common input errors before you finalise the schedule.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"osclf-item osclf-anim\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"osclf-btn\" onclick=\"osclfToggle(this)\"><span class=\"osclf-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Can I use these calculators on mobile?</span><span class=\"osclf-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"osclf-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"osclf-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes. All calculators are mobile-first and work on any browser without downloading an app. Site engineers and supervisors can use them directly from the field on a phone. Results load instantly without any page reload.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"osclf-item osclf-anim osclf-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"osclf-btn\" onclick=\"osclfToggle(this)\"><span class=\"osclf-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How is SiteFlow ERP different from these free calculators?</span><span class=\"osclf-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"osclf-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"osclf-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">These calculators give you a number. SiteFlow ERP manages what happens after that number — procurement orders, material receipts, vendor bills, labour attendance, progress tracking, and live P&amp;L across every project. If you find yourself doing these calculations daily and then manually entering results into Excel or WhatsApp, SiteFlow replaces that entire workflow. The calculators are free because we want to be useful to every construction team, whether or not they use SiteFlow.</p></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n CTA \n<div class=\"osclc-outer\">\n<div class=\"osclc-inner osclf-anim\">\n<div class=\"osclc-eyebrow\"><div class=\"osclc-eyebrow-dot\"></div><span class=\"osclc-eyebrow-txt\">Try SiteFlow ERP</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"osclc-h2\">Good at calculating.<br/><span class=\"osclc-h2-em\">Better at managing.</span></h2>\n<p class=\"osclc-sub\">These calculators save you time on estimates. SiteFlow saves you time on everything else — attendance, materials, billing, and daily reports. Used by construction teams across India and the Middle East.</p>\n<div class=\"osclc-stats\">\n<div class=\"osclc-stat-pill\"><div class=\"osclc-stat-dot\"></div><span class=\"osclc-stat-txt\">10,000+ active clients</span></div>\n<div class=\"osclc-stat-pill\"><div class=\"osclc-stat-dot\"></div><span class=\"osclc-stat-txt\">India and Middle East</span></div>\n<div class=\"osclc-stat-pill\"><div class=\"osclc-stat-dot\"></div><span class=\"osclc-stat-txt\">Live in under 3 days</span></div>\n<div class=\"osclc-stat-pill\"><div class=\"osclc-stat-dot\"></div><span class=\"osclc-stat-txt\">4.8/5 rating</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"osclc-btns\">\n<a class=\"osclc-btn-primary\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">Book a Free Demo →</a>\n<a class=\"osclc-btn-outline\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/SiteFlow-pricing/\">See Pricing</a>\n</div>\n<p class=\"osclc-fine\">No credit card  ·  No commitment  ·  Free onboarding</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n"
}